text: Eustorgius or Eustorge can refer to: *Eustorgius I, bishop of Milan from 344 to 350 *Eustorgius II, bishop of Milan from 512 to 518 *Eustorge de Scorailles, bishop of Limoges from 1106 until 1137 *Eustorgius of Nicomedia, father of Saint Pantaleon *Eustorgius of Montaigu, archbishop of Nicosia in the 13th century ==See also== *Basilica of Sant'Eustorgio
title: Eustorgius
